[b]Information[/b]
Name :- Windows 10 Black 1709 Fall Creators x64
Author :- Kirk
Architecture :- x64
Updates :- 17 October 2017
Activation Status :- PreActivated

[b]Description[/b]
This Windows is Build based on Windows 10 Pro Fall Creators With latest updates of October 2017.

[b]What's Removed :-[/b]
No answer file used, so its not unattended, meaning you choose your account
and settings just like original version.
No settings altered, nothing removed, nothing harmed, UAC disabled for installation of above programs. Shortcut on desktop to re-enable UAC so that Startisback will run with full features

[b]What's Included :-[/b]
[LIST]
[*]Startisback++ 2.52
[*]oldnew explorer preconfigured
[*].netframework 3.5 enabled
[*]ultraUX Theme Patcher 3.3.1
[*]KMSPico for activation
[/LIST]

[b]Install Instruction[/b]
1. Make a Bootable USB/DVD using rufus or any other tool
2. Boot Windows from USB/DVD
3. Follow the on Screen Messages and Finish Intsallation.
4. If it Asks for Key then Click On I don't have a Product Key.
5. Finish the Installation.

[b]Install Note[/b]
Boot with USB or burn to DVD-+R and hit any key then follow the prompts
when asked for key choose no key and continue. On first desktop allow system to
auto reboot to apply theme patcher and Startisback, Re enble UAC (on desktop
shortcut) to use Startisback.
